<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Confirmation - ChessKid Connect</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Confirmation Section -->
    <div class="confirmation-section">
        <h3>Confirmation</h3>
        <p>Your search results have been filtered by chess level and platform (local or online). Parents can contact potential partners using their preferred contact method.</p>
    </div>
    <!-- "What You Can Do Next" Section -->
    <div class="next-steps-section">
        <h3>What You Can Do Next</h3>
        <p>Now that you have your filtered results, feel free to reach out to potential chess partners using their preferred contact method. Connect, play chess, and enjoy!</p>
    </div>
    <ul>
        <% if (data.length > 0) { %>
            <% data.forEach(function(entry) { %>
                <li>
                    <strong>Name:</strong> <%= entry.name %><br>
                    <strong>Email:</strong> <%= entry.email %><br>
                    <strong>Phone Number:</strong> <%= entry.phoneNumber %><br>
                    <strong>Preferred Contact:</strong> <%= entry.contactMethod %><br>
                    <!-- Include other fields as needed -->
                </li>
            <% }); %>
        <% } else { %>
            <p>No matching players found.</p>
        <% } %>
    </ul>
    <!-- Donation Section -->
    <div class="donation-section">
        <h3>Support ChessKid Connect</h3>
        <p>Your donation helps us continue providing a great experience for chess enthusiasts like you. We appreciate your support!</p>
        <label for="donation-amount">Donation Amount:</label>
        <input type="number" id="donation-amount" placeholder="Enter amount">
        <button onclick="showThankYou()">Donate</button>
    </div>

    <script>
        function showThankYou() {
            // Display a thank you message using an alert
            alert("Thank you for your donation!");
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
